    • Method Detail

      • getSuggestions

        AdminSuggestionSearchResult getSuggestions(AdminSuggestion suggestion,
                                           AdminDataDescriptor dataDesc)
                                    throws KKAdminException
        This retrieves AdminSuggestion objects from the database. The suggestion parameter defines the records to be returned.

        The where clause for the select will be created by using the values in the suggestion parameter.

        Parameters:
        suggestion - Used to define the search
        dataDesc - data descriptor for defining generic search parameters such as size and offset
        Returns:
        an AdminSuggestionSearchResult that contains the result of the search
        Throws:
        KKAdminException - an unexpected exception in the KonaKart Admin engine

      • insertSuggestions

        void insertSuggestions(AdminSuggestion[] suggestions)
                throws KKAdminException
        This inserts AdminSuggestion objects into the database. The suggestionType attribute must be set in the AdminSuggestion objects in the array.

        For Product Suggestion types the boughtProductId attribute must be set on the AdminSuggestion objects.

        For Customer Suggestion types the customerId attribute must be set on the AdminSuggestion objects.

        Parameters:
        suggestions - An array of AdminSuggestion objects
        Throws:
        KKAdminException - an unexpected exception in the KonaKart Admin engine

      • deleteSuggestions

        void deleteSuggestions(AdminSuggestion suggestion)
                throws KKAdminException
        This deletes suggestion records from the database. The suggestions that are deleted are defined by the AdminSuggestion record. The where clause for the delete will be created by using the values in the AdminSuggestion.
        Parameters:
        suggestion - An AdminSuggestion object that is used to specify the records to delete.
        Throws:
        KKAdminException - an unexpected exception in the KonaKart Admin engine
